---
title: Sweet Dijon-Glazed Chicken & Bacon Mash with Garlic Veggies
description: Chicken and veggies just got an upgrade! Tender chicken steaks are tossed in dijon mustard and honey for a hit of punchy deliciousness. And this might be our new favourite way to mash - these creamy potatoes are dotted with bacon for the ultimate mash experience.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65ea41f5bbb0ffe7102d1f0d-12319bf3.jpeg
